 of John the Baptist (Luke 1:60). Etymologically, the name means ‘God is my oath’, and is therefore identical with <i>Elisheba</i>, the name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth was born in 1487, in Preston Capes, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Peter Coles. She died after 1522, in Peterborough, Northamptonshire, England."},"et":{"1487–AFT 1522":"1487–pärast 1522","1482–1571":"1482–1571","1510–1575":"1510–1575","1487–1522":"1487–1522","1522":"1522","1510":"1510","AFT 1522":"pärast 1522","1487":"1487","1575":"1575","1571":"1571","1482":"1482","Preston Capes, Northamptonshire, England":"Preston Capes, Northamptonshire, England","Peterborough, Northamptonshire, England":"Peterborough, Northamptonshire, England"},"fi":{"1487–AFT 1522":"1487–1522 jälkeen","1482–1571":"1482–1571","1510–1575":"1510–1575","1487–1522":"1487–1522","1522":"1522","1510":"1510","AFT 1522":"1522 jälkeen","1487":"1487","1575":"1575","1571":"1571","1482":"1482","Preston Capes, Northamptonshire, England":"Preston Capes, Northamptonshire, England","Peterborough, Northamptonshire, England":"Peterborough, Northamptonshire, England"},"fr":{"1487–AFT 1522":"1487–après 1522","1482–1571":"1482–1571","1510–1575":"1510–1575","1487–1522":"1487–1522","1522":"1522","1510":"1510","AFT 1522":"après 1522","1487":"1487","1575":"1575","1571":"1571","1482":"1482","Preston Capes, Northamptonshire, England":"Preston Capes, Northamptonshire, Angleterre","Peterborough, Northamptonshire, England":"Peterborough, Northamptonshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth est née en 1487, à Preston Capes, Northamptonshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Peter Coles. Elle est décédée après 1522, à Peterborough, Northamptonshire, Angleterre."},"de":{"1487–AFT 1522":"1487–nach 1522","1482–1571":"1482–1571","1510–15